    GroundMotionModel (Gmm) identifiers. Use these to generate Imt-specific instances via instance(Imt) and related methods. Single or corporate authored models are identified as NAME_YR_FLAVOR; multi-author models as INITIALS_YR_FLAVOR. FLAVOR is only used for those models with region specific implementations or other variants.
